{"type":null,"faqId":35595,"title":"通话过程中对方听不到或听不清本方说话？","answer":"1.查看下通话时是否本机按了静音；\n\n2.检查下通话时是否手指堵住了MIC孔，MIC孔在手机右下方；\n\n3.不带耳机的情况下，请保持正常握姿，手机有双MIC降噪的功能，如果副MIC离口距离比主MIC近，会导致对方听不到声音；\n\n4.如果带皮套，可以拿掉皮套看下是否有改善；\n\n5.查看出现问题时的信号强度，如果信号较弱，建议移动到信号好的地方，查看是否有明显好转。","faqTypeId":137,"faqType":"通话与联系人","useful":1,"unUseful":8,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"375","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Calls-contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1437124654000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":366,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":3,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀7,honor7,PLK,Plank,通话,音量小","avgScore":3.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}